title: #84:  The Devil in Country With Wheeler Walker Jr
description:
Thank you for to another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. This episode Sam and Ryan welcome country music's favorite outlaw, Wheeler Walker Jr! On this episode we discuss....
1) His podcast, Wheeler Walker Jr, joining All Things Comedy!
2) His upcoming tour with Kid Rock
3) The Gatekeepers of Entertainment
4) Taylor Swift and Zeena Levay
5) Lady GaGa and Lucifer
6) Selling Out
7) Walker Jr sings "If My Dick Is Up Why Am I Down?"
